---
const services = [
  {
    title: 'Asesorías Individualizadas Online',
    description: 'Transformación corporal completa con seguimiento personalizado 24/7. Metodología exclusiva basada en ciencia aplicada y años de experiencia profesional.',
    features: [
      'Plan de entrenamiento 100% personalizado',
      'Asesoramiento nutricional especializado', 
      'Seguimiento diario con feedback inmediato',
      'Videollamadas semanales de seguimiento',
      'Acceso directo vía WhatsApp',
      'Ajustes continuos según tu progreso',
      'Material educativo exclusivo',
      'Garantía de resultados'
    ],
    icon: 'premium'
  }
];
---

<section id="servicios" class="py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-black to-gray-900 text-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-400/20 text-yellow-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4 border border-yellow-400/30">Mis Servicios</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Asesorías <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-yellow-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Personalizadas</span></h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Diseñadas para adaptarse a tu estilo de vida y maximizar tus resultados sin sacrificar equilibrio.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Grid -->
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-16">
      {services.map((s) => (
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-black rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-12 shadow-2xl border-2 border-yellow-400/30 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-yellow-400/20 hover:scale-[1.02] group flex flex-col max-w-2xl w-full ring-2 ring-yellow-400/40 shadow-yellow-400/20">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-yellow-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 shadow-lg shadow-yellow-400/30">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-400/20 text-yellow-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4 border border-yellow-400/40">Servicio Premium</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight text-white">{s.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">{s.description}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-8">
            {s.features.map(f => (
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 0 1-1.414 0l-4-4A1 1 0 0 1 4.707 9.293L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 0 1 1.414 0Z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm leading-relaxed">{f}</span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400/10 to-yellow-500/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-yellow-400/30 mb-6">
              <p class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Resultados Garantizados</p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Metodología probada con más de 500 transformaciones exitosas</p>
            </div>
            <button class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-yellow-500 hover:from-yellow-500 hover:to-yellow-600 text-black font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl text-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-yellow-400/30 hover:shadow-yellow-400/50 hover:scale-[1.02]">
              Solicitar Información
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-black to-neutral-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">¿Listo para comenzar tu transformación?</h3>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Agenda una consulta gratuita de 30 minutos para definir el plan que se adapta realmente a ti.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <button class="bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 active:bg-yellow-600 text-black font-semibold rounded-lg px-8 py-4 text-lg transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">Agendar Consulta</button>
        <button class="border-2 border-yellow-400 text-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-black active:bg-yellow-500 font-semibold rounded-lg px-8 py-4 text-lg transition-all duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-yellow-400 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-black">Enviar WhatsApp</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    const ctaButtons = document.querySelectorAll('#servicios button');
    ctaButtons.forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        document.getElementById('contacto')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
      });
    });
  });
</script>